<% @email_title = "Confirm your eLMo account" %>

<h2>Welcome to eLMo!</h2>

<p>Hello <%= @resource.full_name || @resource.email.split('@').first %>!</p>

<p>Thank you for joining eLMo, your trusted financial partner. We're excited to help you on your financial journey and provide quick, transparent access to the funds you need.</p>

<p>To activate your account and start exploring loan options, please confirm your email address by clicking the button below:</p>

<div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
  <%= link_to 'Confirm My Account', confirmation_url(@resource, confirmation_token: @token), class: 'cta-button' %>
</div>

<div class="info-box">
  <p><strong>What's next?</strong> Once your email is confirmed, you can complete your profile, submit KYC documents, and apply for your first loan. Our streamlined process means you could have funds in minutes, not days!</p>
</div>

<p>This confirmation link will expire in 24 hours for your security. If you don't confirm within this time, you'll need to sign up again.</p>

<div class="alert-box">
  <p><strong>Having trouble?</strong> If the button doesn't work, copy and paste this link into your browser: <%= confirmation_url(@resource, confirmation_token: @token) %></p>
</div>

<p>If you didn't create an eLMo account, please ignore this email and no further action is required.</p>

<p>Welcome aboard!</p>
